column16: Ramon Santiago hits a grand slam (2) to left field.   Todd Frazier scores.    Chris Heisey scores.    Ryan Ludwick scores.
Brayan Pena flies out to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Justin Upton lines out to center fielder Starling Marte.
Joey Terdoslavich doubles (2) on a line drive to center fielder Starling Marte.   Tommy La Stella to 3rd.
Phil Gosselin lines out to center fielder Starling Marte.
Tommy La Stella singles on a line drive to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Freddie Freeman grounds out, second baseman Clint Barmes to first baseman Ike Davis.
Daniel Nava lines out to center fielder Andrew McCutchen.
Cody Asche strikes out swinging, catcher Russell Martin to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Darin Ruf grounds out, third baseman Josh Harrison to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Chris Coghlan flies out to center fielder Starling Marte.
